RACHID BEHNA
Hussein Zuri: Je lui ai aussi tender et mon prix de re-inspection:
1732 25 % gist inf. A. t. fourni 805 o 29.-
213 – 25 % ... m. b. 828 o 38.-
1222-963/ 250 g ... n. l. 841/55 o 86.-

Marché: Écoulement faible, aucun avancement. Il serait à améliorer pour reexporter un peu, car c’est vraiment décourageant; partisans et au bien arranger la situation...

Sous autre forme ce soir: [signature]

René Morand. Le 1er lot qui gagne le trimestre est le N° 78580 (78580)
2e lot L 1000 = 129170.-
3e lot L 500 = 102526.-
4e lot L 250 = 135192.-

J’espère que vous avez eu de ces numéros.
Translation_to_English:
RACHID BEHNA
Hussein Zuri: I have also tendered him and my price for re-inspection:
1732 25 % gist inferior. Delivery supplied 805 at 29.-
213 – 25 % ... m. b. 828 at 38.-
1222-963/ 250 g ... n. l. 841/55 at 86.-

Market: Weak sales, no progress. It should be improved to re-export a little, because it is really discouraging; supporters and to better arrange the situation...

In another form this evening: [signature]

René Morand. The 1st lot that wins the quarter is No. 78580 (78580)
2nd lot £1000 = 129170.-
3rd lot £500 = 102526.-
4th lot £250 = 135192.-

I hope you have some of these numbers.
